OL,3,C23% of parents 'have had to make
OL,4,Ccutbacks to fund school trips'
OL,6,FThe "bank of gran and grandad" is
OL,7,Fhelping to fund some school trips,
OL,8,Fwith nearly a quarter of parents
OL,9,Fsaying they have had to make cutbacks
OL,10,Fto afford them, a survey has found.
OL,12,FSome 23% of parents surveyed for
OL,13,Fpublic sector insurer Zurich Municipal
OL,14,Fsaid they have had to go without and
OL,15,Fperhaps cut back on essentials to fund
OL,16,Fschool trips.
