OL,6,FFamily members have also been giving a
OL,7,Fhelping hand, with one in 10 (10%)
OL,8,Fparents surveyed saying grandparents
OL,9,Fhad paid for their child's school trip
OL,10,Fand 8% of parents saying their child's
OL,11,Faunt or uncle stepped in.
OL,13,FThe research also indicated that one
OL,14,Fin eight (12%) children have taken
OL,15,Fpart in fundraising activities
OL,16,Fthemselves to help cover the costs of
OL,17,Ftrips, and a further one in 10 have
OL,18,Fused their pocket money.
